<div class="container">
  <div class="ctas text-center">
<h3>Solving the Food Wastage Problem in NYC one connection at a time</h3>
{{#bs-alert type="info"}}
  Register as a Donor or a Recipient to view our Listings
{{/bs-alert}}


{{#bs-modal open=openModal title="Register"}}
   <center>Please Sign up or Login to View Listings</center>
   <br><br>
   <center>
   {{#link-to 'signup' class="btn btn-success"}} SignUp {{/link-to}}
   {{#link-to 'login' class="btn btn-success"}} Login {{/link-to}}
 </center>
 {{/bs-modal}}

<div class="row">
  <div class="col-md-6">
    {{#link-to 'signup' (query-params type="Donor") class="btn btn-success"}}
    I Have Food
    {{/link-to}}
  </div>
  <div class="col-md-6">
    {{#link-to 'signup' (query-params type="Recipient") class="btn btn-success"}}
    I Need Food
    {{/link-to}}
  </div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>

<div class="belowthefold">
<center><h2>How It Works</h2></center>
<div class="row">
  <div class="col-sm-6 col-md-6">
    <div class="thumbnail">
      <img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/6/64/Foods_%28cropped%29.jpg" alt="Donors" class="img-thumbnail img-responsive firstimage" style="object-fit:cover">
      <div class="caption">
        <h3>Donors</h3>
        <p>Local Restaurants and Cafes let us know what type of food they have and when someone can come pick them</p>
        {{#link-to 'signup' (query-params type="Donor") class="btn btn-primary"}}Donors {{/link-to}}
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="col-sm-6 col-md-6">
    <div class="thumbnail">
      <img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/1/15/US_Navy_111123-N-HW977-185_Sailors_weigh_Thanksgiving_food_drive_donations_before_delivery_to_the_Corona-Norco_Settlement_House.jpg" alt="Recipients" class="img-thumbnail img-responsive">
      <div class="caption">
        <h3>Recipients</h3>
        <p>Local nonprofits can see the what, where and when of food surplus options, and fix a time to pick up the food</p>
        {{#link-to 'signup' (query-params type="Recipient") class="btn btn-primary"}}Recipients{{/link-to}}
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

</div>
